{"tid":1161904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呀媽想我幫佢借錢，點算？","createTime":"2019-05-19T13:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T15:39:26.000Z","uid":84818,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5e151bca996ee4d6a101e77da7e8dd4b38ee5e","tid":1161904,"uid":84818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"事源係我媽媽以前破過產，前幾個月識左d人做咩咩塑身內衣代理人，自己又想做埋一份但冇錢，於是想洗底問銀行借低息貸款。佢之前聽人講可以比錢洗底，向另一間財仔借左兩萬幾蚊諗住去洗底，咁當然係洗唔到啦，咁佢咪死死氣去借財仔十萬買內衣做代理人。加埋都十六、七萬，但係佢自己又冇草開錢，三個月前仲要quiz埋正職，依家返緊炒散，每個月得萬六、七蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢一個月開支大約：9xxx（安信）、3xxx（仁貴）、6500（租）、生活費。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後因爲佢欠落幾個月租，就來比人趕走，但係因為佢誠信太差，冇朋友親戚肯借比佢，佢又返緊炒散冇糧單借唔到錢，係咁勸我問銀行低息借錢，佢每個月還返比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我未必借唔到，但係真係好驚佢唔還錢又再問財仔借錢。。。重點係我係fresh grad, 人工得萬六蚊仲要養埋老豆細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位絲打巴打覺得我應唔應該幫佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2999a7624cbd28af9f30c290db2933bb70a283f6","tid":1161904,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"quiz埋 唔撚睇落去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cbe4a92cb64e7818d5ece1e3c4bfc2b9e17a44","tid":1161904,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"不了，越借會越大"},{"pid":"4bda92763f71e74ddb5e770456dd8a8459305a81","tid":1161904,"uid":84818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2999a7624cbd28af9f30c290db2933bb70a283f6","tid":1161904,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"quiz埋 唔撚睇落去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚到打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acdb3331bf7c0ee8c81ecc36fbed008fe139282","tid":1161904,"uid":175668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"千其咪撚幫佢借"},{"pid":"04dfb02845e82e58252813ffd969bc54b7b3ceda","tid":1161904,"uid":31788,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"唔好，之前就係幫左屋企人借十幾萬<br />\n還完一排又要我再拎，唔拎就話我冇血性乜乜乜<br />\n早2，3年銀行终於唔俾我再拎<br />\n我先可以安心咁還錢<br />\n話就話幫佢借，但佢一蚊都冇還過。<br />\n仲係啲親戚朋友面前話我俾得少家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b14cf849718b7596c267639f41e61f7609f6bca","tid":1161904,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7e1b778f9c286e7d87683c60520e8af6247d71","tid":1161904,"uid":31788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"真心勸你唔好<br />\n我係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其佢冇固定工作同埋開支咁大<br />\n覺得佢會有錢還俾你咩？"},{"pid":"77fad4b9936fb1b139f2f24b35b8dbec016b0f02","tid":1161904,"uid":84818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb7e1b778f9c286e7d87683c60520e8af6247d71","tid":1161904,"uid":31788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"真心勸你唔好<br />\n我係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其佢冇固定工作同埋開支咁大<br />\n覺得佢會有錢還俾你咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢還唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹因爲佢係我呀媽，唔幫佢好似好冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫左就害自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8cd113c7e37f274e4f6c19aaf1bc086482cea6","tid":1161904,"uid":65984,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"人不為己 天誅地滅, 唔係話狠心到唔幫佢借, 但都要睇餸食飯<br />\n佢有生意頭腦既, 就唔會一把年紀都身無分文<br />\n佢有養育過你, 但你絕對唔係佢提款機<br />\n如果佢話, 係有養育過你, 所以你要回報返佢, 咁就純粹當你係投資產品, 以後可以同佢撇清關係<br />\n如果佢只係想你盡幫, 你咪預左佢唔還, 計下自己未來一年可以還幾多, 你咪幫佢借幾多<br />\n人既青春. 發展期好短, 唔好為左其他人而拖累自己, 就算屋企人都咁話, 唔係你一定會後悔"},{"pid":"981b22eb1f8a932fe3125a617d8f34dd8dd5f150","tid":1161904,"uid":7567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"借左你成家一齊仆街，唔借大家辛苦d幾年時間還清果十幾萬，開開心心咁生活，破過一次產都唔識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a6ffef26a268a8918149e2c8ffc81f45ba62e4","tid":1161904,"uid":31788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77fad4b9936fb1b139f2f24b35b8dbec016b0f02","tid":1161904,"uid":84818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb7e1b778f9c286e7d87683c60520e8af6247d71","tid":1161904,"uid":31788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"真心勸你唔好<br />\n我係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其佢冇固定工作同埋開支咁大<br />\n覺得佢會有錢還俾你咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢還唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹因爲佢係我呀媽，唔幫佢好似好冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫左就害自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"我就係害咗自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年我入不付支到過哂期<br />\n銀行要我即刻還晒所有欠款<br />\n好彩傾掂數每個月還多$1000<br />\n我依家出嘅糧，就係還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過還到九月終於還完<br />\n我斷斷續續還左差唔多九年<br />\n其實正常四年已經玩完<br />\n但中途又有幾次攞過錢出嚟<br />\n某程度上我好感激銀行突然要入息證明先可以再拎款<br />\n如果唔係真係沒完沒了"},{"pid":"c70b7444315218a663ba3b97cec6938e53dc60b7","tid":1161904,"uid":31788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"我成日同佢講⋯<br />\n你冇錢你都有我幫你問銀行借<br />\n我差唔多成30歲人男朋友有冇⋯<br />\n都唔望第時會結到婚<br />\n都我有事嗰陣邊個可以幫我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d2bfb2c7d8089cf8486452a454c9277637f54b","tid":1161904,"uid":95847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好，之前就係幫左屋企人借十幾萬<br />\n還完一排又要我再拎，唔拎就話我冇血性乜乜乜<br />\n早2，3年銀行<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">终</span></span>於唔俾我再拎<br />\n我先可以安心咁還錢<br />\n話就話幫佢借，但佢一蚊都冇還過。<br />\n仲係啲親戚朋友面前話我俾得少家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fa77782bc276bbc7ea6bbac00ce19f79adf85411","tid":1161904,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"長貧難顧"},{"pid":"c98729412fe8bf7e1f6ea24284073fe77623e89e","tid":1161904,"uid":145923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好，佢所謂既生意，可以話衰過賭錢，賭錢都有機會贏，佢比錢去做呢D所謂生意就蝕硬，你留番個錢，等佢唔掂到無飯開時，比飯佢食比地方佢住，作為仔女，做到咁就足夠！"},{"pid":"0ff251c4b0138436522fd94a7f87d20ac1a5db48","tid":1161904,"uid":96502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"過來人<br />\n咪撚借,借左一定唔會還足"},{"pid":"b807db6baf1db5b592c716e8e034910482119c63","tid":1161904,"uid":156547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"幫佢借拎黎做咩？純粹交租定比佢繼續投資檔生意？<br />\n如果你真心想幫佢，唔好比錢過佢手，幫佢交租/支票寫業主名，同埋要講明只幫佢呢次同講明交幾多個月<br />\n我覺得咁已經盡左你做仔女既責任"},{"pid":"c0624f06fa123f2a502e7b69322ec3f1630548a7","tid":1161904,"uid":254364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"一定唔會係最後一次，今次借左還唔到之餘仲會繼續有其他新債。今次比佢又借到錢過關，佢以後唔會識解決問題，只會一味借錢找數，你唔係幫佢係害佢，仲要自己爭落身債"},{"pid":"80c8210f7e6d9e14d22d7e8c8bdebb58922e0cdf","tid":1161904,"uid":254364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"佢有心想翻身既，自己乖乖地返工break even 番，先再用自己錢做新生意啦。"},{"pid":"3c2f5f413342a9d3bbe91aeb74f3c7291b08c13b","tid":1161904,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77fad4b9936fb1b139f2f24b35b8dbec016b0f02","tid":1161904,"uid":84818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb7e1b778f9c286e7d87683c60520e8af6247d71","tid":1161904,"uid":31788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"真心勸你唔好<br />\n我係過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其佢冇固定工作同埋開支咁大<br />\n覺得佢會有錢還俾你咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢還唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹因爲佢係我呀媽，唔幫佢好似好冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫左就害自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"咁你打算點"},{"pid":"8592cb13e7990eb9a7623b32e3423923a54c6ca8","tid":1161904,"uid":55758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:26:35.000Z","msg":"你當佢係阿媽 但佢有無當你係仔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b1fff13a490bf7c352ee71deca1be1555e1ecc","tid":1161904,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"唔好呀屌<br />\n我老母當年為咗幫大舅父還貴利，迫我老豆同銀行借錢<br />\n條撚樣還唔足，變成我屋企幫佢還債<br />\n我老豆又搵唔多、結果舊數碌撚到大一大<br />\n仲要影響埋我屋企本來嘅生活"},{"pid":"d2004512131a7d7407506b034c5a098b4c137fc0","tid":1161904,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"借比佢<br />\n但叫佢買定份人壽, 受益人寫你<br />\n同佢講自殺過左一年投保就會有派彩<br />\n你一年內唔還就自己識做"},{"pid":"f23610223cfe0053930951f50e01cddb5e4bb6ba","tid":1161904,"uid":252593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"不了，順便叫佢醒下啦"}]}